```py
# cd into SQLAlchemy source distribution
cd path/to/sqlalchemy

# install cython
pip install cython

# optionally build Cython extensions ahead of install
python setup.py build_ext

# run the install
python setup.py install
```

```py
# cd into SQLAlchemy source distribution
cd path/to/sqlalchemy

# install build
pip install build

# build source / wheel dists
python -m build
```
